headline: Defense Secretary Hegseth Cuts Take Down Booz Allen and Other Contractor Stocks
summary: Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth announced more defense cuts.  Secretary Hegseth announced and signed an order to eliminate $580 million in contracts and grants on Thursday afternoon.  Contracts for  Gartner  and McKinsey were mentioned by name.
